What you need to know:

Restoration of ancient machines brings out the qualities of patience and meticulousness to their purest forms and no hamlet in the four corners of the earth is too far to search for partsSati Jabbal’s home resembles a Doughty showroom in its heyday only that his collection includes every imaginable model. Currently, he is shopping for space to continue feeding his passionGata-Aura is today one of the most consistent participants in the Concourse d’Elegance and his immaculate 1947 green and cream MGT is a real gem 